Extra Virgin Americana - Season 1, Episode 4




Shark Sighting on the Cape

Debi Mazar takes her family to the Mayflower replica in Cape Cod, Mass., to show them a piece of their family history. They also have lunch at the Sunbird Food Truck, and go on Gabriele Corcos's planned adventure -- oyster farming! They end their trip with some quintessential Cape Cod family fun on the beach.




Original Air Date: 23-Mar-2016
